kpi.name: M1006C268

kpi_info.title: CANCELLED INTRA-BTS LAYER CHANGES IN PCH/FACH TO DCH
kpi_info.use: The number of intra-BTS frequency layer changes in PCH to Cell_DCH transition cancelled because of CPICH RSCP quality check. The counter is updated for the cell where the UE was located before the state transition attempt. UPDATED: When inter-frequency PCH to Cell_DCH is cancelled because of CPICH RSCP value sent by the UE in RRC: Cell Update does not fulfill the quality check criteria.
